{"text_id":35420,"tokens":["The"," debate"," on"," whether"," schools"," should"," require"," students"," to"," maintain"," a"," B"," average"," in"," order"," to"," participate"," in"," sports"," or"," extracurricular"," activities"," is"," a"," complex"," one",","," with"," valid"," arguments"," on"," both"," sides","."," On"," one"," hand",","," implementing"," such"," a"," policy"," could"," have"," numerous"," benefits",","," including"," encouraging"," academic"," excellence",","," promoting"," time"," management"," skills",","," and"," ensuring"," that"," students"," prioritize"," their"," studies","."," On"," the"," other"," hand",","," it"," could"," also"," lead"," to"," increased"," stress"," and"," anxiety",","," as"," well"," as"," limiting"," opportunities"," for"," students"," who"," may"," not"," excel"," academically"," but"," have"," talents"," and"," skills"," in"," other"," areas",".","\n\n","From"," my"," perspective",","," schools"," should"," not"," require"," students"," to"," maintain"," a"," B"," average"," in"," order"," to"," participate"," in"," sports"," or"," extracurricular"," activities","."," While"," academics"," are"," undoubtedly"," important",","," it"," is"," crucial"," to"," recognize"," and"," nurture"," a"," student","'","s"," holistic"," development",","," which"," includes"," their"," physical",","," emotional",","," and"," social"," growth","."," Ex","cluding"," students"," from"," extracurricular"," activities"," based"," solely"," on"," their"," academic"," performance"," could"," have"," long","-","lasting"," negative"," consequences",","," such"," as"," damaging"," their"," self","-","esteem"," and"," hindering"," their"," overall"," development",".","\n\n","Instead",","," schools"," should"," focus"," on"," providing"," students"," with"," the"," necessary"," tools"," and"," resources"," to"," succeed"," in"," both"," academics"," and"," extracurricular"," activities","."," This"," can"," include"," offering"," academic"," support"," and"," tutoring"," programs",","," promoting"," time"," management"," skills",","," and"," creating"," a"," supportive"," and"," inclusive"," environment"," that"," encourages"," students"," to"," strive"," for"," excellence"," in"," all"," areas"," of"," their"," lives","."," Ultimately",","," by"," fostering"," a"," well","-","rounded"," education",","," schools"," can"," help"," students"," develop"," the"," skills"," and"," confidence"," they"," need"," to"," succeed"," both"," in"," and"," out"," of"," the"," classroom","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}